statement: I hold myself to very high standards and always strive to do what is right and ethical.
I feel most fulfilled when I am helping others, often putting their needs above my own.
I am driven to succeed and often focus on how others perceive my accomplishments.
I often feel different from others and express myself in unique and creative ways.
I value my privacy and spend a lot of time observing and analyzing the world around me.
I am often anxious and seek security by being loyal and responsible in my relationships and commitments.
I love seeking out new, exciting experiences and sometimes struggle with staying focused.
I am confident and assertive, often taking control of situations to make sure things are done correctly.
I strive to keep the peace and often go along with others to avoid conflict.
